Package fifoanimalshelter

Class FIFOAnimalShelter

  • java.lang.Object
    • fifoanimalshelter.FIFOAnimalShelter
  • public class FIFOAnimalShelter
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a queue based (FIFO) data structure whose nodes are animal names. The standard queue operations of enqueue and dequeue are supported. Except, they work with animal arguments. It doesn't support generics, and is a learning based implementation that only stores the name of an animal, not the animal object itself.
